about.summary: A database interface definition for communication between R and relational database management systems.  All classes in this package are virtual and need to be extended by the various R/DBMS implementations.

name: r-dbi
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '1.0.0' %}

{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-dbi
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  fn: DBI_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/DBI_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/DBI/DBI_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: ff16f118eb3f759183441835e932b87358dd80ab9800ce576a8f3df1b6f01cf5

build:
  noarch: generic
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1002

  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{posix}}zip               # [win]

  host:
    - r-base

  run:
    - r-base

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('DBI')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('DBI')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://r-dbi.github.io/DBI
  license: LGPL (>= 2)
  summary: A database interface definition for communication between R and relational database
    management systems.  All classes in this package are virtual and need to be extended
    by the various R/DBMS implementations.
  license_family: LGPL
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/LGPL-2'  # [unix]
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}\R\share\licenses\LGPL-2'  # [win]

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - johanneskoester
    - bgruening
    - daler
    - jdblischak
    - cbrueffer
    - dbast
